  <div class="page">
    <h1>From Luttappi — A Hasty Letter</h1>

    <div class="letter">
      <p>Brothers Kuttusan and Dakini,</p>

      <p>I write in haste — I found Mayavi resting under an old banyan by the eastern trail. The night air smelled of salt and lantern-smoke; she sleeps light. I thought it best to wake you both immediately, but the hours thinned and the moon hid its face.</p>

      <p>Rally at the clearing marked by three stones (just beyond the old well). Bring only the seals — no torches. If you hurry, you can catch the whisper before dawn.</p>

      <p>— Luttappi</p>

      <p class="meta">(Login: try user <strong>luttappi</strong> — portal limited. This page contains a note; some words may not be truthful.)</p>
    </div>

